lob_price_dfs = []
day_i = 20200902

for skey_i in tqdm(skey_list[:100]):
    price_df = factor_dao.read_factor_by_skey_and_day(factor_group='lob_static_price_factors',
                                                      skey=skey_i, day=day_i, version='v1')
    index_df = factor_dao.read_factor_by_skey_and_day(factor_group='index_factors',
                                                      skey=skey_i, day=day_i, version='v1')
    if price_df is not None and index_df is not None:
        price_df = price_df.merge(index_df, on=['skey', 'date', 'time', 'ordering', 'minute'])
        lob_price_dfs.append(price_df)

lob_price_dfs = pd.concat(lob_price_dfs, ignore_index=True)
lob_price_dfs = lob_price_dfs.loc[~lob_price_dfs.nearLimit]
print(lob_price_dfs.shape)
